          <p class='first-para'>
            Will the hon. Gentleman give way?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0361P0_20010117_WH_135'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-simon-burns' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
