          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-simon-burns" title="Mr Simon Burns">Mr. Burns</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            No; I shall mention Swindon shortly.</p><p>
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_137wh' title='Col. 137WH &mdash; HC Deb 17 January 2001 vol 361 c137WH' name='column_137wh' href='#column_137wh' rel='bookmark'>137WH</a>
            Reading, with a population of 143,000, is well below the threshold. Swindon is not well below, but is still below, the threshold.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0361P0_20010117_WH_136'>  </a>
