            Apparently it also has a well-publicised rivalry with Reading, so I shall let the hon. Members for South Swindon and for Reading, East (Jane Griffiths) fight it out among themselves.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0361P0_20010117_WH_139'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-julia-drown' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
